data.description: ELEGANT AND EXQUISITE! This stunning home located in the gorgeous community of Redtail is now available. Picture driving home everyday from work and as you enter the community, you are welcomed home by oak canopy line roads that bring instant peace and serenity. As you pull into the driveway of your new home you notice immediately all of the room you have for parking in your brick paver driveway. Attention to detail was not skipped anywhere in this home. As you are welcomed through the front door, the open and airy floor plan will catch your eye. The large living room features a  beautiful stone accent wall and glass sliders. Gorgeous kitchen with granite counter tops and top of the line appliances overlooks the living area and eat in space. The formal dining is a great place to host dinner parties and also has a built in bar. Romantic master suite with double door entry features a large room, his and her closets, a garden tub with separate walk in shower as well has separate vanities. Split bedroom plan with rooms #2 and #3 has a jack and jill connecting bath. Bedroom #4 currently used as an office with beautiful custom built ins and double door entry. A half bath is convenient for your guests. The garage in this home has all the room and more that you would need and more for all of your vehicles and toys. You will love to entertain in this amazing back porch area complete with a stunning pool and flush overflowing hot tub. A couple great features to the pool is that it can be heated either gas or electric and has lounging areas with holes built in to hold umbrellas that allow adequate shade on those hot summer days. The outdoor kitchen area with built in grill and mini refrigerator is great to host gatherings at complete with a  outdoor dining area and adorable pool bath. Completely fenced in backyard. In this gorgeous community you will find top notch amenities such as a golf course, restaurant, gym and community pool. There is so much to continue to say about this stunning home...come see for yourself. Be prepared to fall in love with this one!
